      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ARMATREE PASTA (1) is racing well without winning, recording three minors on end, the latest hitting the ground running with a scorching early sectional but finishing in the minors again over 431m at this track, clocking 24.75. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. One of the leading chances. ARMATREE JUDO (3) won by 2 lengths last start when getting around this track 340m in a dominant 19.44. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. CASUAL ESCAPE (2) turned in a moderate run last time when sixth at this track over 431m behind Laurie's Ferrari (25.30) in a Grade 5. Has a strong record out of this box with three wins and a minor placing from six starts. Can measure up this time. VICTOR CARGO (7) produced a powerful 19.59 when filling a minor placing last start. Can measure up with a repeat.",
